data.description: Welcome home to one of the most convenient neighborhoods in all of Moody. This 3 bedroom home features a large den with recess lighting. It features an eat-in kitchen which includes an island, pantry, breakfast bar, new stainless steel appliances, light fixtures, and a desk area. 3 spacious bedrooms are found at one end of the home which includes the master, full bath, and a half bath. Don't forget the cozy light filled living room as you enter plus the BONUS room that can be used as another den, mancave, extra bedroom, exercise, study, etc... The possibilities are only limited by your imagination. The large fenced back yard is perfect for children or pets with plenty of room to run and play. This home has many updates including but not limited to windows, hvac, flooring, and appliances. This is a great home in a great neighborhood only a few minutes walk to the Moody Municipal Park. Schedule your tour today!!
